264 852 1157 (     Of course, const Iterator is different from const_iterator and from) 1157 SB
264 952 1132 (    This change was accepted in Monterey \(see N740\).  However, in) 1132 SB
264 1002 1066 (    box 108, Corfield says it seems wrong to have const member) 1066 SB
